20\r\n00:12:08,020 --> 00:12:09,770\r\nNo. No, no, no.\r\nI'll find a way.\r\n\r\n221\r\n00:12:09,771 --> 00:12:11,439\r\nOkay, so make the changes\r\nto the PowerPoint,\r\n\r\n222\r\n00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,149\r\nand let's meet again at 2:30.\r\n\r\n223\r\n00:12:13,150 --> 00:12:14,484\r\nOkay.\r\n\r\n224\r\n00:12:22,201 --> 00:12:24,369\r\nLeave a message\r\nfor Frank Underwood.\r\n\r\n225\r\n00:12:25,621 --> 00:12:27,121\r\nIt's me.\r\n\r\n226\r\n00:12:27,122 --> 00:12:29,165\r\nI feel like an idiot\r\nleaving messages like this.\r\n\r\n227\r\n00:12:29,166 --> 00:12:30,791\r\nCall me back.\r\n\r\n228\r\n00:12:42,679 --> 00:12:43,804\r\nWhat is it, Zoe?\r\n\r\n229\r\n00:12:43,805 --> 00:12:45,806\r\nUm...\r\n\r\n230\r\n00:12:45,807 --> 00:12:47,934\r\nI know you're going to have your\r\nhands full at the white house,\r\n\r\n231\r\n00:12:47,935 --> 00:12:51,145\r\nso if you need someone\r\nto do research or...\r\n\r\n232\r\n00:12:51,146 --> 00:12:52,480\r\nOr print out background...\r\n\r\n233\r\n00:12:52,481 --> 00:12:54,148\r\nI think I'll be fine.\r\n\r\n234\r\n00:12:54,149 --> 00:12:56,735\r\nWell, if things get hectic\r\nand you need any help...\r\n\r\n235\r\n00:12:56,736 --> 00:13:00,947\r\nSo you can blog about rubbing\r\nshoulders with the big boys?\r\n\r\n236\r\n00:13:03,908 --> 00:13:05,368\r\nWhat did Lucas tell you?\r\n\r\n237\r\n00:13:05,369 --> 00:13:07,328\r\nLook, no offense, Zoe,\r\nbut I don't have time\r\n\r\n238\r\n00:13:07,329 --> 00:13:09,581\r\nto be anyone's training wheels.\r\n\r\n239\r\n00:13:09,582 --> 00:13:11,958\r\nI just thought...\r\n\r\n240\r\n00:13:11,959 --> 00:13:14,586\r\nNo, I was actually offering\r\nto lend a hand.\r\n\r\n241\r\n00:13:14,587 --> 00:13:16,337\r\n- That's it.\r\n- Got it.\r\n\r\n242\r\n00:13:16,338 --> 00:13:18,047\r\nThanks.\r\n\r\n243\r\n00:13:58,045 --> 00:13:59,922\r\n- Claire.\r\n- You didn't call.\r\n\r\n244\r\n00:13:59,923 --> 00:14:03,301\r\n- I was...\r\n- You didn't call me, Francis.\r\n\r\n245\r\n00:14:03,302 --> 00:14:05,762\r\nNine hours.\r\nYou don't not call me,\r\n\r\n246\r\n00:14:05,763 --> 00:14:07,430\r\nnot when it's this big.\r\n\r\n247\r\n00:14:07,431 --> 00:14:08,765\r\nYou're right.\r\n\r\n248\r\n00:14:08,766 --> 00:14:11,810\r\nWhen have we ever avoided each other?\r\n\r\n249\r\n00:14:13,770 --> 00:14:15,772\r\nI wanted the solution first.\r\n\r\n250\r\n00:14:15,773 --> 00:14:17,190\r\nDo you have one?\r\n\r\n251\r\n00:14:17,191 --> 00:14:19,066\r\nNot yet.\r\n\r\n252\r\n00:14:19,067 --> 00:14:21,110\r\nThis affects me, too, Francis.\r\n\r\n253\r\n00:14:21,111 --> 00:14:24,071\r\nAnd it's not the money I'm upset about.\r\n\r\n254\r\n00:14:24,072 --> 00:14:26,741\r\nIt's that we do things together.\r\n\r\n255\r\n00:14:26,742 --> 00:14:29,410\r\nWhen you don't involve me,\r\nwe're in free-fall.\r\n\r\n256\r\n00:14:29,411 --> 00:14:32,163\r\nI should've called you, and I didn't.\r\n\r\n257\r\n00:14:32,164 --> 00:14:33,581\r\nWhat happened?\r\n\r\n258\r\n00:14:34,999 --> 00:14:37,377\r\nShe says they needed\r\nto keep me in congress.\r\n\r\n259\r\n00:14:37,378 --> 00:14:38,586\r\nLinda said that?\r\n\r\n260\r\n00:14:38,587 --> 00:14:39,796\r\nWalker wasn't even there.\r\n\r\n261\r\n00:14:39,797 --> 00:14:41,381\r\nThat's what really gets me.\r\n\r\n262\r\n00:14:41,382 --> 00:14:43,216\r\nHe didn't have the courage\r\nto look me in the eye.\r\n\r\n263\r\n00:14:43,217 --> 00:14:44,967\r\nI knew you shouldn't trust that woman.\r\n\r\n264\r\n00:14:44,968 --> 00:14:46,720\r\nI didn't. I don't.\r\nI don't trust anyone.\r\n\r\n265\r\n00:14:46,721 --> 00:14:48,888\r\nThen how could you not see this coming?\r\n\r\n266\r\n00:14:50,432 --> 00:14:52,559\r\nI never thought they were capable.\r\n\r\n267\r\n00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:55,436\r\nYou don't usually\r\nunderestimate people, Francis.\r\n\r\n268\r\n00:14:55,437 --> 00:14:56,730\r\nI know.\r\n\r\n269\r\n00:14:58,231 --> 00:15:00,817\r\nHubris. Ambition.\r\n\r\n270\r\n00:15:00,818 --> 00:15:02,026\r\nYou shou