ake a train...\r\n\r\n714\r\n00:42:20,498 --> 00:42:22,540\r\nJust before you left my house...\r\n\r\n715\r\n00:42:22,541 --> 00:42:24,209\r\nThink back...\r\n\r\n716\r\n00:42:24,210 --> 00:42:26,002\r\nWhat were we discussing?\r\n\r\n717\r\n00:42:27,212 --> 00:42:28,921\r\nThe president's legislative agenda.\r\n\r\n718\r\n00:42:28,922 --> 00:42:30,840\r\nSpecifically.\r\n\r\n719\r\n00:42:30,841 --> 00:42:32,967\r\nEducation. Was I right?\r\n\r\n720\r\n00:42:32,968 --> 00:42:35,594\r\nDo the math, miss Barnes.\r\n\r\n721\r\n00:42:35,595 --> 00:42:38,806\r\n- He needs a bill.\r\n- Sponsored by...\r\n\r\n722\r\n00:42:38,807 --> 00:42:42,519\r\n- You?\r\n- Be smarter than that.\r\n\r\n723\r\n00:42:44,729 --> 00:42:46,523\r\n- Somebody with legitimacy.\r\n- Good.\r\n\r\n724\r\n00:42:46,524 --> 00:42:49,775\r\nAnd who screams legitimacy\r\nand education?\r\n\r\n725\r\n00:42:49,776 --> 00:42:52,653\r\n- Donald blythe?\r\n- Correct. The problem is...\r\n\r\n726\r\n00:42:52,654 --> 00:42:55,614\r\nHe's an old-school\r\ntax-and-spend liberal.\r\n\r\n727\r\n00:42:55,615 --> 00:42:58,326\r\nWalker ran as a moderate.\r\n\r\n728\r\n00:42:59,702 --> 00:43:02,080\r\nYou think blythe would talk to me?\r\n\r\n729\r\n00:43:03,081 --> 00:43:05,208\r\nHe doesn't have to.\r\n\r\n730\r\n00:43:06,751 --> 00:43:09,170\r\nWait. We're in\r\na very gray area...\r\n\r\n731\r\n00:43:09,171 --> 00:43:11,923\r\nEthically, legally...\r\nWhich I'm okay with...\r\n\r\n732\r\n00:43:11,924 --> 00:43:14,509\r\nI just love this painting.\r\nDon't you?\r\n\r\n733\r\n00:43:16,052 --> 00:43:18,471\r\nWe're in the same boat now, Zoe.\r\n\r\n734\r\n00:43:18,472 --> 00:43:20,014\r\nTake care not to tip it over.\r\n\r\n735\r\n00:43:20,015 --> 00:43:22,975\r\nI can only save one of us from drowning.\r\n\r\n736\r\n00:43:49,668 --> 00:43:52,171\r\nHe announces his education\r\ninitiative on Monday.\r\n\r\n737\r\n00:43:52,172 --> 00:43:54,591\r\n- Half of the address is based on...\r\n- I understand.\r\n\r\n738\r\n00:43:54,592 --> 00:43:56,926\r\n- Do we need to take it out?\r\n- We're fine, Linda.\r\n\r\n739\r\n00:43:56,927 --> 00:43:59,387\r\nBut you just got through\r\nsaying he has to start over.\r\n\r\n740\r\n00:43:59,388 --> 00:44:01,347\r\nI didn't choose blythe.\r\nYou did.\r\n\r\n741\r\n00:44:01,348 --> 00:44:04,100\r\nYou put him in my lap and asked\r\nme to work a miracle, and I will.\r\n\r\n742\r\n00:44:04,101 --> 00:44:06,144\r\nNow, have a little faith, Linda.\r\n\r\n743\r\n00:44:06,145 --> 00:44:07,728\r\nLet me work with Donald on this.\r\n\r\n744\r\n00:44:07,729 --> 00:44:10,440\r\nI know what can be\r\naccomplished in 100 days.\r\n\r\n745\r\n00:44:10,441 --> 00:44:13,485\r\nAll right, Frank.\r\nWe're counting on you.\r\n\r\n746\r\n00:44:13,486 --> 00:44:15,194\r\nGood.\r\n\r\n747\r\n00:44:16,571 --> 00:44:18,531\r\nNow, I do have a little favor to ask.\r\n\r\n748\r\n00:44:18,532 --> 00:44:21,951\r\nDo you think I can get\r\njust two more tickets\r\n\r\n749\r\n00:44:21,952 --> 00:44:25,288\r\nfor my table at the Jefferson ball?\r\n\r\n750\r\n00:44:35,173 --> 00:44:38,676\r\n- Drink?\r\n- Uh, sure! What do you got?\r\n\r\n751\r\n00:44:38,677 --> 00:44:40,094\r\nWhiskey. Blend.\r\n\r\n752\r\n00:44:40,095 --> 00:44:42,930\r\nIf you're offering.\r\n\r\n753\r\n00:44:42,931 --> 00:44:45,642\r\nSo... how are things\r\n\r\n754\r\n00:44:45,643 --> 00:44:47,393\r\nin the city of brotherly love?\r\n\r\n755\r\n00:44:47,394 --> 00:44:50,188\r\n- We're getting by.\r\n- Oh, good.\r\n\r\n756\r\n00:44:50,189 --> 00:44:52,273\r\nGood. Oh, I'm sorry.\r\n\r\n757\r\n00:44:52,274 --> 00:44:55,360\r\n- I made that neat. Did you want...\r\n- No, this is perfect.\r\n\r\n758\r\n00:45:05,161 --> 00:45:09,499\r\nSo, it seems you've been\r\na bit irresponsible.\r\n\r\n759\r\n00:45:09,500 --> 00:45:11,250\r\nWhat?\r\n\r\n760\r\n00:45:11,251 --> 00:45:13,336\r\nDon't play dumb with me, Peter.\r\n\r\n761\r\n00:45:13,337 --> 00:45:15,463\r\nSave it for the ethics committee.\r\n\r\n762\r\n00:45:16,964 --> 00:45:19,634\r\nDrink up. You could use\r\na little courage right now.\r\n\r\n763\r\n00:45:19,635 --> 00:45:22,136\r\nYou're not having one.\r\n\r\n764\r\n00:45:22,137 --> 00:45:25,390\r\nIt's a bit early in the day for me.\r\n\r\n765\r\n00:45:27,184 --> 00:45:29,519\r\nIs this about the other night?\r\n\r\n766\r\n00:45:29,520 --> 00:45:30,936\r\nHow do you know about that?\r\n\r\n767\r\n00:45:30,937 --> 00:45:33,730\r\nI'm the whip.\r\nIt's my job to know.\r\n\r\n768\r\n00:45:33,731 --> 00:45:35,525\r\nLook... look, they let me off.\r\n\r\n769\r\n00:45:35,526 --> 00:45:38,486\r\nThere's... there's no charges.\r\nIt's all taken care of.\r\n\r\n770\r\n00:45:38,487 --> 00:45:40,488\r\nHonestly, Peter,\r\n\r\n771\r\n00:45:40,489 --> 00:45:42,198\r\ndo you really think these things\r\n\r\n772\r\n00:45:42,199 --> 00:45:44,116\r\njust take care of themselves?\r\n\r\n773\r\n00:45:44,117 --> 00:45:46,785\r\nYou...\r\n\r\n774\r\n00:45:49,081 --> 00:45:51,790\r\nIt was just this one time,\r\nFrank. I swear to God.\r\n\r\n775\r\n00:45:51,791 --> 00:45:54,001\r\nThen you must hold God\r\nin very low esteem,\r\n\r\n776\r\n00:45:54,002 --> 00:45:57,213\r\nbecause we both know that's a lie.\r\n\r\n777\r\n00:45:57,214 --> 00:46:00,717\r\n\"Solicitation, controlled substances,\r\n\r\n778\r\n00:46:00,718 --> 00:46:03,094\r\ndriving under the influence.\"\r\n\r\n779\r\n00:46:03,095 --> 00:46:05,888\r\nGot quite a long list of hobbies.\r\n\r\n780\r\n00:46:07,265 --> 00:46:09,726\r\nWhat is it you want?\r\n\r\n781\r\n00:46:20,027 --> 00:46:25,700\r\nYour absolute, unquestioning loyalty.\r\n\r\n782\r\n00:46:25,701 --> 00:46:27,201\r\nAlways.\r\n\r\n783\r\n00:46:27,202 --> 00:46:31,205\r\nDo not misunderstand\r\nwhat I mean by \"loyalty.\"\r\n\r\n784\r\n00:46:31,206 --> 00:46:34,125\r\nAnything. Name it, Frank.\r\n\r\n785\r\n00:46:34,126 --> 00:46:37,712\r\n- You seem far too relaxed.\r\n- I'm not.\r\n\r\n786\r\n00:46:37,713 --> 00:46:39,922\r\nYou shouldn't be.\r\n\r\n787\r\n00:46:41,758 --> 00:46:44,093\r\nDoug'll be in touch.\r\n\r\n788\r\n00:46:48,307 --> 00:46:49,682\r\nHang on.\r\n\r\n789\r\n00:46:49,683 --> 00:46:51,643\r\nWhere have you been?\r\nI've been calling you.\r\n\r\n790\r\n00:46:51,644 --> 00:46:53,561\r\nEverybody's working double-time\r\nin an inauguration,\r\n\r\n791\r\n00:46:53,562 --> 00:46:56,063\r\nand you just up and disappear...\r\n\r\n792\r\n00:46:57,106 --> 00:46:59,525\r\nHang on.\r\n\r\n793\r\n00:47:05,239 --> 00:47:06,991\r\nLet me call you back.\r\n\r\n794\r\n00:47:10,495 --> 00:47:12,913\r\n- Where did you get this?\r\n- Wrong question.\r\n\r\n795\r\n00:47:12,914 --> 00:47:16,501\r\nThe right question is, how quickly\r\ncan we get it up on the site?\r\n\r\n796\r\n00:47:16,502 --> 00:47:19,170\r\nI have to run this past tom.\r\n\r\n797\r\n00:47:19,171 --> 00:47:20,963\r\nLet's get legal on this.\r\n\r\n798\r\n00:47:20,964 --> 00:47:23,341\r\nMake sure we're not breaking any laws.\r\n\r\n799\r\n00:47:23,342 --> 00:47:25,884\r\n- You won't tell me your source?\r\n- I can't do that.\r\n\r\n800\r\n00:47:25,885 --> 00:47:28,554\r\n- Fine, but if legal finds even one...\r\n- I understand.\r\n\r\n801\r\n00:47:28,555 --> 00:47:31,223\r\nHow long do you think that will take?\r\nWe should get this online right away.\r\n\r\n802\r\n00:47:31,224 --> 00:47:33,267\r\nI'm not just going to scan\r\na 300-page document\r\n\r\n803\r\n00:47:33,268 --> 00:47:35,060\r\nand put it up before we\r\nhave gone through every...\r\n\r\n804\r\n00:47:35,061 --> 00:47:37,814\r\n- I did that already.\r\n- The whole thing?\r\n\r\n805\r\n00:47:37,815 --> 00:47:39,940\r\nCover to cover.\r\nI've got excerpts, analysis.\r\n\r\n806\r\n00:47:39,941 --> 00:47:42,276\r\n3,000 words ready for editing.\r\n\r\n807\r\n00:47:43,820 --> 00:47:45,279\r\nYou start going over them.\r\n\r\n808\r\n00:47:45,280 --> 00:47:47,406\r\nGet graphics. Work on\r\nthe tables, charts...\r\n\r\n809\r\n00:47:47,407 --> 00:47:50,034\r\nThe whole nine yards.\r\n\r\n810\r\n00:47:50,035 --> 00:47:51,868\r\nJanine!\r\n\r\n811\r\n00:47:51,869 --> 00:47:53,830\r\nWhat's the angle? Five words.\r\n\r\n812\r\n00:47:53,831 --> 00:47:55,998\r\n- Far left of center.\r\n- That's four.\r\n\r\n813\r\n00:47:55,999 --> 00:47:58,751\r\n- Very far left of center.\r\n- Enough to put Walker on his heels?\r\n\r\n814\r\n00:47:58,752 --> 00:48:00,378\r\nFuck his heels.\r\nThis'll put him on his ass.\r\n\r\n815\r\n00:48:00,379 --> 00:48:02,254\r\nWhat's up?\r\n\r\n816\r\n00:48:02,255 --> 00:48:05,090\r\nWe've got a copy of the\r\nadministration's education bill.\r\n\r\n817\r\n00:48:05,091 --> 00:48:07,760\r\n- You're going to work with Zoe and do background cover.\r\n- Zoe Barnes?\r\n\r\n818\r\n00:48:07,761 --> 00:48:10,638\r\n- Right here.\r\n- Whatever she needs.\r\n\r\n819\r\n00:48:10,639 --> 00:48:13,057\r\n- Well, shouldn't I be writing the...\r\n- She wrote it already.\r\n\r\n820\r\n00:48:13,058 --> 00:48:15,434\r\nAnd I want you to rewrite it,\r\nthen rewrite it again.\r\n\r\n821\r\n00:48:15,435 --> 00:48:18,145\r\n- You'll help her.\r\n- Tom, I am your chief political correspondent.\r\n\r\n822\r\n00:48:18,146 --> 00:48:20,189\r\nGo! I want this by tomorrow.\r\n\r\n823\r\n00:48:20,190 --> 00:48:22,692\r\n- But I need to focus on the inauguration.\r\n- This is more important.\r\n\r\n824\r\n00:48:22,693 --> 00:48:24,861\r\nLet's get started.\r\n\r\n825\r\n00:48:24,862 --> 00:48:26,903\r\n\"That I will\r\nfaithfully execute the office\"\r\n\r\n826\r\n00:48:26,904 --> 00:48:28,740\r\nof president\r\nof the United States.\"\r\n\r\n827\r\n00:48:28,741 --> 00:48:30,742\r\nThat I will faithfully\r\nexecute the office...\r\n\r\n828\r\n00:48:30,743 --> 00:48:32,577\r\nPower is a lot like real estate.\r\n\r\n829\r\n00:48:32,578 --> 00:48:35,996\r\nIt's all about location,\r\nlocation, location.\r\n\r\n830\r\n00:48:35,997 --> 00:48:37,832\r\nThe closer you are to the source,\r\n\r\n831\r\n00:48:37,833 --> 00:48:39,542\r\nthe higher your property value.\r\n\r\n832\r\n00:48:39,543 --> 00:48:41,502\r\n\"And defend\r\nthe constitution...\"\r\n\r\n833\r\n00:48:41,503 --> 00:48:44,296\r\nCenturies from now,\r\nwhen people watch this footage,\r\n\r\n834\r\n00:48:44,297 --> 00:48:47,508\r\nwho will they see smiling\r\njust at the edge of the frame?\r\n\r\n835\r\n00:48:47,509 --> 00:48:50,177\r\n- \"So help me God.\"\r\n- So help me God.\r\n\r\n836\r\n00:48:50,178 --> 00:48:52,054\r\nCongratulations.\r\n\r\n837\r\n00:49:08,613 --> 00:49:13,033\r\nToday... is not about\r\nthe next four years.\r\n\r\n838\r\n00:49:13,034 --> 00:49:16,287\r\nIt's about the next four decades.\r\n\r\n839\r\n00:49:16,288 --> 00:49:19,123\r\nNow, you've placed your faith in me,\r\n\r\n840\r\n00:49:19,124 --> 00:49:21,125\r\nand I, in turn,\r\n\r\n841\r\n00:49:21,126 --> 00:49:25,087\r\nchoose to place that faith\r\nin our children.\r\n\r\n842\r\n00:49:25,088 --> 00:49:30,217\r\nOur children are the key\r\nto this nation's future.\r\n\r\n843\r\n00:49:30,218 --> 00:49:32,804\r\nAnd that's why\r\nthe first order of business\r\n\r\n844\r\n00:49:32,805 --> 00:49:34,513\r\nfor this administration\r\n\r\n845\r\n00:49:34,514 --> 00:49:38,183\r\nwill be a comprehensive\r\neducation reform bill\r\n\r\n846\r\n00:49:38,184 --> 00:49:41,978\r\nto properly fix, finance,\r\n\r\n847\r\n00:49:41,979 --> 00:49:45,232\r\nand strengthen our nation's schools!\r\n\r\n848\r\n00:49:48,152 --> 00:49:50,696\r\nAnd I pledge to you,\r\n\r\n849\r\n00:49:50,697 --> 00:49:53,908\r\nwe will have that bill\r\non the floor of the congress\r\n\r\n850\r\n00:49:53,909 --> 00:49:58,329\r\nwithin the first 100 days\r\nof this administration!\r\n\r\n851\r\n00:50:03,751 --> 00:50:06,170\r\nIt was so nice of you\r\nto make this possible.\r\n\r\n852\r\n00:50:06,171 --> 00:50:07,964\r\n- When you called me, I was...\r\n- Oh, not another one.\r\n\r\n853\r\n00:50:07,965 --> 00:50:09,715\r\nI'm gonna miss out\r\n\r\n854\r\n00:50:09,716 --> 00:50:12,301\r\non my ultimate frisbee league this week.\r\n\r\n855\r\n00:50:12,302 --> 00:50:14,720\r\nNo, I'm serious.\r\nA few of us on budget\r\n\r\n856\r\n00:50:14,721 --> 00:50:17,682\r\nhave quite a rivalry going\r\nwith the guys on finance.\r\n\r\n857\r\n00:50:17,683 --> 00:50:20,309\r\nIt's fierce. We get physical.\r\n\r\n858\r\n00:50:20,310 --> 00:50:22,227\r\nAnybody gets between me\r\nand that goal line,\r\n\r\n859\r\n00:50:22,228 --> 00:50:25,481\r\nI will take that sucker down!\r\n\r\n860\r\n00:50:45,626 --> 00:50:48,253\r\nDonald, I've been looking\r\nfor you everywhere.\r\n\r\n861\r\n00:50:48,254 --> 00:50:50,715\r\nMaestro, here, let me\r\nhelp you out with this.\r\n\r\n862\r\n00:50:50,716 --> 00:50:52,884\r\nI really like the work\r\nyou've done on the new draft.\r\n\r\n863\r\n00:50:52,885 --> 00:50:55,386\r\nIt's a big step forward. We're\r\ngonna make history together.\r\n\r\n864\r\n00:50:55,387 --> 00:50:57,471\r\nThanks for the encouragement.\r\nFrancis, listen...\r\n\r\n865\r\n00:50:57,472 --> 00:50:59,765\r\nI've got some ideas about\r\nsubsidies for higher education...\r\n\r\n866\r\n00:50:59,766 --> 00:51:02,476\r\nCatherine! Hold onto\r\nthat thought, Donald.\r\n\r\n867\r\n00:51:02,477 --> 00:51:05,437\r\nDon't you look stunt!\r\n\r\n868\r\n00:51:05,438 --> 00:51:08,315\r\nWe Southern girls clean up well\r\nwhen we get out of our Daisy Dukes\r\n\r\n869\r\n00:51:08,316 --> 00:51:11,569\r\n- and into some vera wang.\r\n- And we Southern boys are slow with our words,\r\n\r\n870\r\n00:51:11,570 --> 00:51:13,445\r\nbut we're fast on our feet.\r\n\r\n871\r\n00:51:13,446 --> 00:51:15,197\r\nMay I have the honor?\r\n\r\n872\r\n00:51:15,198 --> 00:51:17,366\r\nYou most certainly may.\r\n\r\n873\r\n00:51:42,016 --> 00:51:44,309\r\n- Mornin', Freddy.\r\n- Good morning, Frank.\r\n\r\n874\r\n00:51:44,310 --> 00:51:46,812\r\n- How's tricks?\r\n- I can't kick.\r\n\r\n875\r\n00:51:46,813 --> 00:51:49,648\r\n- You want to go on in?\r\n- No. Why don't you set me up outside?\r\n\r\n876\r\n00:51:49,649 --> 00:51:51,901\r\nOutside?\r\nIt's freezing out here.\r\n\r\n877\r\n00:51:51,902 --> 00:51:54,486\r\nWell, a little cold never hurt anybody.\r\n\r\n878\r\n00:51:54,487 --> 00:51:56,530\r\nAnything you say, Frank.\r\n\r\n879\r\n00:51:56,531 --> 00:51:58,783\r\nIt'll be right up.\r\n\r\n880\r\n00:51:58,784 --> 00:52:01,994\r\nMy one guilty pleasure is a good rack\r\nof ribs, even at 7:30 in the morning.\r\n\r\n881\r\n00:52:01,995 --> 00:52:03,871\r\nHave the whole place to myself.\r\n\r\n882\r\n00:52:03,872 --> 00:52:05,539\r\nFreddy sometimes opens up just for me.\r\n\r\n883\r\n00:52:05,540 --> 00:52:07,792\r\nWhere I come from in South Carolina,\r\n\r\n884\r\n00:52:07,793 --> 00:52:10,294\r\npeople didn't have\r\ntwo pennies to rub together.\r\n\r\n885\r\n00:52:10,295 --> 00:52:13,297\r\nA rack of ribs is a luxury, like...\r\n\r\n886\r\n00:52:16,467 --> 00:52:19,386\r\nChristmas in July.\r\n\r\n887\r\n00:52:57,215 --> 00:52:59,760\r\nThis web traffic's absolutely crazy.\r\n\r\n888\r\n00:53:03,555 --> 00:53:07,601\r\nBlue Camry, D.C.\r\nPlate number whiskey, Juliet, 0-0-2-niner\r\n\r\n889\r\n00:53:07,602 --> 00:53:10,186\r\nis wanted in connection\r\nto a canine hit-and-run.\r\n\r\n890\r\n00:53:10,187 --> 00:53:13,189\r\nCode 1057, found on capital...\r\n\r\n891\r\n00:53:13,190 --> 00:53:14,566\r\nMmm.\r\n\r\n892\r\n00:53:14,567 --> 00:53:16,027\r\nDo you want seconds, Frank?\r\n\r\n893\r\n00:53:16,028 --> 00:53:18,320\r\nI'd better not.\r\n\r\n894\r\n00:53:19,279 --> 00:53:21,406\r\nTell you what, Freddy...\r\n\r\n895\r\n00:53:21,407 --> 00:53:23,659\r\nYes, I will.\r\n\r\n896\r\n00:53:23,660 --> 00:53:26,704\r\nI'm feeling hungry today.\r\n\r\n","markerStore":{"nextMarkerId":132,"markersById":{"0":{"range":{"start":{"row":27,"column":1},"end":{"row":27,"column":1}},"properties":{"type":"selection","editorId":8,"preserveFolds":true,"goalScreenRange":null},"reversed":false,"tailed":false,"valid":true,"invalidate":"never","maintainHistory":true}},"version":2},"history":{"version":2